er were allowed at the Beijing Games.\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No spectators\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"a limited number\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing Games\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Comparatively, there were no formal requirements for regular COVID-19 testing or reporting for the Paris Games, either in general or for specific events.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2049, \"end\": 2065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_testing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.495303238388502e-27, \"text\": \"COVID-19 testing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_testing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_testing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no formal requirements\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"specific events\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An athlete testing positive did not require them to sit out from an event either.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An athlete testing\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Participating following a positive test was left up to the discretion of the athlete, team and medical staff.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a positive test\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"the discretion\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"team\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"medical staff\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, there were no restrictions regarding spectators.\",